Class BaseInterest

  • java.lang.Object
    • cz.cuni.mff.kocur.base.Location

  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Camp, Fort, Fountain, Healer, NeutralSpawner, PathCorner, Rax, Rune, Shop, Tower

    public class BaseInterest
extends Location
    Class that represents a BaseInterest. This class stores informations, that are already not inside Location and that might be usefull to interest objects.
    Author:
    kocur
